  "title": "ADMINISTRATOR",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Type general correspondence.</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing proposals, progress claims, variation orders.</li>\n  <li>Compile and submit equipment and catalogue for project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Assist to request and submit materials requisitions to purchasing department for project’s requirements.</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper filing for every project undertaken.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate work with Project Manager/Engineer on site matters (e.g. scheduled meetings, workers’ name list submission, delivery of items/materials to work site, etc.)</li>\n  <li>Keep confidential material classified and take steps to improve documentation whenever possible.</li>\n  <li>Any other general administrative work assigned by the Project Manager and/or Engineer.</li>\n  <li>Any other duties that may be assigned by the company.</li>\n</ul>",
